eeePC Fan Control - Perl Daemon

-----Requirements-----
- Perl
- eee.ko Module (http://code.google.com/p/eeepc-linux/)

-----Installation-----
cp eeepc-fancontrol /usr/bin/:
chmod a+x /usr/bin/eeepc-fancontrol

mv eeepc-fancontrol-init /etc/init.d/eeepc-fancontrol
update-rc.d eeepc-fancontrol defaults

/etc/init.d/eeepc-fancontrol start